  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Vibrant Palette\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Vibrant Palette\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#FEF9EC] flex flex-col overflow-hidden font-sans text-slate-800\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-20 bg-white border-b border-orange-100 flex items-center justify-between px-10 shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6 text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129\\\"></path></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900\\\">Igbo<span class=\\\"text-orange-500\\\">Sync</span></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex bg-orange-50 rounded-full p-1 border border-orange-100\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-white rounded-full shadow-sm text-sm font-semibold text-orange-600\\\">Translator</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500\\\">History</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Settings</button>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 border-l pl-6 border-orange-100\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Model Active</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-mono text-orange-600\\\">whisper-large-v3-igbo</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-200 border-2 border-white shadow-sm\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Workspace -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 flex flex-col gap-8\\\">\\n    <!-- Language Selector Bar -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white px-8 py-3 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-orange-50 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold\\\">English</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600\\\">\\n          <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4\\\"></path></svg>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold\\\">Igbo</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Translation Interface -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8\\\">\\n      <!-- Input Section -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-[32px] border border-orange-100 shadow-xl p-8 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Input Source</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <textarea class=\\\"w-full flex-1 text-2xl font-medium text-slate-700 bg-transparent resize-none focus:outline-none placeholder:text-slate-300\\\" placeholder=\\\"Type here or start recording...\\\">How is the weather today in Lagos? I hope it\'s not raining too much.</textarea>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mt-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl text-slate-400 hover:text-orange-500\\\">\\n              <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z\\\"></path></svg>\\n            </button>\\n            <button class=\\\"p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl text-slate-400\\\">\\n              <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewB